# No secrets are required to build this site.
#
# BASE_PATH is only needed when deploying under a sub-path
# (e.g. GitHub Pages project site). CI sets this automatically.
# BASE_PATH=/AI_Forum_Website_v3
#
# The Web3Forms access key is public-by-design (it identifies the inbox,
# not a secret) and lives in src/lib/config.ts. Restrict it to your
# domain in the Web3Forms dashboard. See CONTENT-TODO.md.
